title: Bong-Ra - Sick Sick Sick
description:
Drumcorps did a great job on "Grist" to mix Deathcore and Breakcore together but Bong-Ra went 19 steps further!  Bong-ra took riffs from Slayer and others to create a sheer masterpiece of sonic and noise devastation.  These tracks later appear on the "Full Metal Racket" cd but this is just the first part of the two Eps he released creating a masterpiece.
